[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":530},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20260113\u002F3115395907\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20260113\u002F3115395907\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20260113\u002F3115395907\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20260113\u002F3115395907\u002F":505,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20260113\u002F3115395907\u002F":514},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2026\u002F01\u002F13\u002Frun-multiple-commands-with-concurrently\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":488,"date":489,"description":25,"extension":490,"lang":491,"meta":492,"navigation":162,"path":493,"readingMinutes":494,"seo":495,"standalone":496,"stem":497,"tags":498,"tldr":502,"updated":489,"url":503,"__hash__":504},"content\u002FNodejs\u002F真是受夠開多個終端機執行多個指令了！來用-concurrently-吧.md","真是受夠開多個終端機執行多個指令了！來用 concurrently 吧","3115395907",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":481},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,30,33,45,48,82,85,100,106,110,121,207,216,310,317,320,323,389,395,398,405,467,477],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"concurrently","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fnode-concurrently\u002FGemini_Generated_Image_u5lg8zu5lg8zu5lg.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"隨著手上負責的專案越來越多，我也開始需要同時開啟多個終端機視窗來執行不同的指令，例如前端專案的開發伺服器、後端 API 伺服器、資料庫服務等等。每次都要手動開啟多個終端機視窗並輸入指令，實在是非常麻煩且浪費時間，所以這一篇來介紹一下 concurrently 這個工具。",[20,27,29],{"id":28},"concurrently-是什麼","concurrently 是什麼？",[12,31,32],{},"簡單來說，它是一個能讓你「平行」執行多個指令的工具。",[12,34,35,36,40,41,44],{},"很多人會嘗試使用 ",[37,38,39],"code",{},"watch-js"," && ",[37,42,43],{},"watch-css","，但這其實是序列執行（Sequential），必須等前一個指令完成（結束進程）後，才會跑下一個，像 watch 類型或開發伺服器的指令是永遠不會結束的，這導致後面的指令被阻塞，你只好乖乖開好幾個終端機視窗來執行這些指令。",[12,46,47],{},"那為了解決這件事情變成打開一個專案就要開數個終端機視窗，以我曾經接手的專案中，就有開啟這幾個指令的需求：",[49,50,51,58,64,70,76],"ul",{},[52,53,54,57],"li",{},[37,55,56],{},"npm run dev:backend","：後端 API 伺服器",[52,59,60,63],{},[37,61,62],{},"npm run dev:ejs","：前端 EJS 模板伺服器",[52,65,66,69],{},[37,67,68],{},"npm run watch:styles","：監聽 CSS 檔案變化",[52,71,72,75],{},[37,73,74],{},"npm run watch:scripts","：監聽 JavaScript 檔案變化",[52,77,78,81],{},[37,79,80],{},"npm run db:server","：資料庫服務",[12,83,84],{},"雖然前端的部分可以直接改用 Webpack 、Vite、Gulp 這些工具來同時監聽這些檔案變化，但是後端跟資料庫相關卻還是沒有辦法整合進去，所以還是需要開啟多個終端機視窗來執行這些指令。",[12,86,87,88,90,91,90,94,96,97,99],{},"因此至少至少還是會需要開啟三個終端機視窗（",[37,89,56],{},"、",[37,92,93],{},"npm run dev:frontend",[37,95,80],{},"）來執行這些指令，這樣就會讓我覺得非常麻煩且浪費時間，所以這邊就要來介紹 ",[37,98,17],{}," 這個工具。",[12,101,102,103,105],{},"而 ",[37,104,17],{}," 重點就是讓你可以一個終端機視窗中，同時執行多個指令，並且可以自動管理這些指令的輸出，讓你可以輕鬆地看到每個指令的執行狀態。",[20,107,109],{"id":108},"concurrently-怎麼用","concurrently 怎麼用？",[12,111,112,113,116,117,120],{},"使用方式非常的簡單，這邊我會非常建議直接安裝進去你的專案中，這樣就可以直接在 ",[37,114,115],{},"package.json"," 中的 ",[37,118,119],{},"scripts"," 區塊中使用，儘管官方有提供全域安裝的方式，不過我個人還是比較建議安裝在專案中，這樣可以確保每個專案使用的版本是一致的。",[122,123,128],"pre",{"className":124,"code":125,"language":126,"meta":127,"style":127},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","# npm\nnpm install concurrently --save-dev\n\n# yarn\nyarn add concurrently --dev\n\n# pnpm\npnpm add concurrently --save-dev\n","bash","",[37,129,130,139,157,164,170,184,189,195],{"__ignoreMap":127},[131,132,135],"span",{"class":133,"line":134},"line",1,[131,136,138],{"class":137},"sGBqm","# npm\n",[131,140,142,146,150,153],{"class":133,"line":141},2,[131,143,145],{"class":144},"smYoP","npm",[131,147,149],{"class":148},"sWayO"," install",[131,151,152],{"class":148}," concurrently",[131,154,156],{"class":155},"stw71"," --save-dev\n",[131,158,160],{"class":133,"line":159},3,[131,161,163],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":162},true,"\n",[131,165,167],{"class":133,"line":166},4,[131,168,169],{"class":137},"# yarn\n",[131,171,173,176,179,181],{"class":133,"line":172},5,[131,174,175],{"class":144},"yarn",[131,177,178],{"class":148}," add",[131,180,152],{"class":148},[131,182,183],{"class":155}," --dev\n",[131,185,187],{"class":133,"line":186},6,[131,188,163],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":162},[131,190,192],{"class":133,"line":191},7,[131,193,194],{"class":137},"# pnpm\n",[131,196,198,201,203,205],{"class":133,"line":197},8,[131,199,200],{"class":144},"pnpm",[131,202,178],{"class":148},[131,204,152],{"class":148},[131,206,156],{"class":155},[12,208,209,210,212,213,215],{},"安裝完畢後，打開你的 ",[37,211,115],{}," 檔案，在 ",[37,214,119],{}," 區塊中加入一個新的指令，例如：",[122,217,221],{"className":218,"code":219,"language":220,"meta":127,"style":127},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","\"scripts\": {\n  \"dev:all\": \"concurrently \\\"npm run dev:frontend\\\" \\\"npm run dev:backend\\\" \\\"npm run db:server\\\"\",\n  \"dev:frontend\": \"webpack serve\",\n  \"dev:backend\": \"node server.js\",\n  \"dev:db\": \"mongod --dbpath .\u002Fdata\u002Fdb\"\n}\n","json",[37,222,223,232,271,283,295,305],{"__ignoreMap":127},[131,224,225,228],{"class":133,"line":134},[131,226,227],{"class":148},"\"scripts\"",[131,229,231],{"class":230},"s8XSl",": {\n",[131,233,234,238,241,244,248,250,252,255,257,259,261,263,265,268],{"class":133,"line":141},[131,235,237],{"class":236},"sWTrB","  \"dev:all\"",[131,239,240],{"class":230},": ",[131,242,243],{"class":148},"\"concurrently ",[131,245,247],{"class":246},"sbsOT","\\\"",[131,249,93],{"class":148},[131,251,247],{"class":246},[131,253,254],{"class":246}," \\\"",[131,256,56],{"class":148},[131,258,247],{"class":246},[131,260,254],{"class":246},[131,262,80],{"class":148},[131,264,247],{"class":246},[131,266,267],{"class":148},"\"",[131,269,270],{"class":230},",\n",[131,272,273,276,278,281],{"class":133,"line":159},[131,274,275],{"class":236},"  \"dev:frontend\"",[131,277,240],{"class":230},[131,279,280],{"class":148},"\"webpack serve\"",[131,282,270],{"class":230},[131,284,285,288,290,293],{"class":133,"line":166},[131,286,287],{"class":236},"  \"dev:backend\"",[131,289,240],{"class":230},[131,291,292],{"class":148},"\"node server.js\"",[131,294,270],{"class":230},[131,296,297,300,302],{"class":133,"line":172},[131,298,299],{"class":236},"  \"dev:db\"",[131,301,240],{"class":230},[131,303,304],{"class":148},"\"mongod --dbpath .\u002Fdata\u002Fdb\"\n",[131,306,307],{"class":133,"line":186},[131,308,309],{"class":230},"}\n",[12,311,312,313,316],{},"這樣你就可以透過 ",[37,314,315],{},"npm run dev:all"," 來同時執行這三個指令，並且可以在同一個終端機視窗中看到這三個指令的輸出。",[20,318,319],{"id":319},"使用萬用字元簡化指令",[12,321,322],{},"如果你的 scripts 命名很有規律，可以進一步簡化：",[122,324,326],{"className":218,"code":325,"language":220,"meta":127,"style":127},"\"scripts\": {\n  \"dev:all\": \"concurrently \\\"npm run dev:*\\\"\",\n  \"dev:frontend\": \"webpack serve\",\n  \"dev:backend\": \"node server.js\",\n  \"dev:db\": \"mongod --dbpath .\u002Fdata\u002Fdb\" \n}\n",[37,327,328,334,353,363,373,385],{"__ignoreMap":127},[131,329,330,332],{"class":133,"line":134},[131,331,227],{"class":148},[131,333,231],{"class":230},[131,335,336,338,340,342,344,347,349,351],{"class":133,"line":141},[131,337,237],{"class":236},[131,339,240],{"class":230},[131,341,243],{"class":148},[131,343,247],{"class":246},[131,345,346],{"class":148},"npm run dev:*",[131,348,247],{"class":246},[131,350,267],{"class":148},[131,352,270],{"class":230},[131,354,355,357,359,361],{"class":133,"line":159},[131,356,275],{"class":236},[131,358,240],{"class":230},[131,360,280],{"class":148},[131,362,270],{"class":230},[131,364,365,367,369,371],{"class":133,"line":166},[131,366,287],{"class":236},[131,368,240],{"class":230},[131,370,292],{"class":148},[131,372,270],{"class":230},[131,374,375,377,379,382],{"class":133,"line":172},[131,376,299],{"class":236},[131,378,240],{"class":230},[131,380,381],{"class":148},"\"mongod --dbpath .\u002Fdata\u002Fdb\"",[131,383,384],{"class":230}," \n",[131,386,387],{"class":133,"line":186},[131,388,309],{"class":230},[390,391,392],"blockquote",{},[12,393,394],{},"這樣 concurrently 就會自動抓取所有以 dev: 為前綴的指令並同時執行唷。",[20,396,397],{"id":397},"自動結束其他指令",[12,399,400,401,404],{},"最後這邊介紹一個 ",[37,402,403],{},"kill-others"," 指令，這個指令可以讓你在其中一個指令結束（意指發生錯誤）時，自動結束其他指令",[122,406,407],{"className":218,"code":325,"language":220,"meta":127,"style":127},[37,408,409,415,433,443,453,463],{"__ignoreMap":127},[131,410,411,413],{"class":133,"line":134},[131,412,227],{"class":148},[131,414,231],{"class":230},[131,416,417,419,421,423,425,427,429,431],{"class":133,"line":141},[131,418,237],{"class":236},[131,420,240],{"class":230},[131,422,243],{"class":148},[131,424,247],{"class":246},[131,426,346],{"class":148},[131,428,247],{"class":246},[131,430,267],{"class":148},[131,432,270],{"class":230},[131,434,435,437,439,441],{"class":133,"line":159},[131,436,275],{"class":236},[131,438,240],{"class":230},[131,440,280],{"class":148},[131,442,270],{"class":230},[131,444,445,447,449,451],{"class":133,"line":166},[131,446,287],{"class":236},[131,448,240],{"class":230},[131,450,292],{"class":148},[131,452,270],{"class":230},[131,454,455,457,459,461],{"class":133,"line":172},[131,456,299],{"class":236},[131,458,240],{"class":230},[131,460,381],{"class":148},[131,462,384],{"class":230},[131,464,465],{"class":133,"line":186},[131,466,309],{"class":230},[12,468,469,470,476],{},"當然你還可以高度客製化這些指令的輸出方式，這部份我就不詳細介紹了，我認為你可以直接參考官方文件：",[471,472,17],"a",{"href":473,"rel":474},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.npmjs.com\u002Fpackage\u002Fconcurrently",[475],"nofollow","。",[478,479,480],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sGBqm, html code.shiki .sGBqm{--shiki-light:#6A737D;--shiki-default:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .smYoP, html code.shiki .smYoP{--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-default:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sWayO, html code.shiki .sWayO{--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-default:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .stw71, html code.shiki .stw71{--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-default:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#91CBFF}html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decorat